"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/834273","Department of Health and Social Care","false","2018-02-07","<p>The Department has one contract with Capita taken from the Crown Commercial Services Contingent Labour One Framework. The value of the contract is £45 million.</p><p> </p><p>This information is based on data held in the Department’s contract register.</p>","Gosport","Caroline Dinenage",,"2018-02-07T16:54:06.157Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/834273/answer","Biography information for Caroline Dinenage","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/834273/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/834273/answer",,,,,"17","Health and Social Care","Health and Social Care","2018-01-31","Department of Health and Social Care: Capita","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Health and Social Care, how many contracts his Department holds with Capita; and what the total value of those contracts is.","false","Biography information for Jon Trickett","Hemsworth","Jon Trickett","125894"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/834275","Home Office","false","2018-02-07","<p>The Home Office currently holds 3 contracts with Capita, with a total contract value of £309m. <br>The Home Office has since 2010, published details of its contracts over 10K on the Pan-Gov’t Contracts Finder portal, as part of the HMT Transparency Agenda. The link to the portal is as follows: <a href="https://www.gov.uk/contracts-finder" target="_blank">https://www.gov.uk/contracts-finder </a></p>","Louth and Horncastle","Victoria Atkins",,"2018-02-07T16:29:57.817Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/834275/answer","Biography information for Victoria Atkins","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/834275/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/834275/answer",,,,,"1","Home Office","Home Office","2018-01-31","Home Office: Capita","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for the Home Department, how many contracts her Department holds with Capita; and what the total value of those contracts is.","false","Biography information for Jon Trickett","Hemsworth","Jon Trickett","125895"
