"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/834277","Department for Digital, Culture, Media and Sport","false","2018-02-20","<p>DCMS calls down from a cross-Government Framework agreement held by the Crown Commercial Service (Contingent Labour One). The spend on this for the financial year 2017/2018 is £3.5million.</p>","Stourbridge","Margot James",,"2018-02-20T16:43:25.873Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/834277/answer","Biography information for Margot James","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/834277/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/834277/answer",,,,,"10","Digital, Culture, Media and Sport","Digital, Culture, Media and Sport","2018-01-31","Department for Digital, Culture, Media and Sport: Capita","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Digital, Culture, Media and Sport, how many contracts his Department holds with Capita; and what the value of those contracts is.","false","Biography information for Jon Trickett","Hemsworth","Jon Trickett","125897"
